[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0825","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0825.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0562","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 空会话远程注册表访问漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 存在空会话（Null Session）远程访问注册表的权限漏洞。未经身份认证的攻击者可通过 SMB 协议建立空会话连接，远程匿名访问目标系统的注册表，获取系统配置、用户账户信息、网络共享设置等敏感数据。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 所有 SP 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。Microsoft 至今未完全移除该默认行为，需通过修改注册表或限制 IPC$ 访问进行缓解。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0562"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:38.693","remediation":"升级到 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a，并设置注册表项 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\LSA 下的 RestrictAnonymous 值为 2，禁止空会话枚举 SAM 账号和共享。同时禁用 NetBIOS over TCP/IP，在防火墙层面阻止 137-139、445 端口的外部入站连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A1023","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19372","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0562.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0562","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0562.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0562.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0562.json","https://github.com/Azure/Azure-Sentinel/blob/c359f282ec6bc3eb6912ee4649970789e923d257/Sample%20Data/Custom/beSECURE_ScanResults_CL.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8954696320cbff8f7d95f98854cf0e72222fc646/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6wh7-hrcm-fv9m/GHSA-6wh7-hrcm-fv9m.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/smb_registry_access.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0562.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_1.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0825.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0824","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0824.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0991","title":"GoodTech Telnet Server NT 缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"GoodTech Telnet Server NT 2.2.1 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器的 Telnet 服务发送超长的登录名字符串触发该漏洞，导致服务器进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 GoodTech Telnet Server NT 2.2.1 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。攻击无需身份认证，利用难度较低，但仅能导致服务不可用，无法实现远程代码执行。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0991"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-06T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:28.577","remediation":"建议立即升级 GoodTech Telnet Server NT 至高于 2.2.1 的修复版本；如厂商已停止支持，请迁移至其他受维护的 Telnet/SSH 服务端软件（如 Windows OpenSSH）。临时缓解措施：在防火墙层面限制 TCP 端口 23 的入站连接，仅允许受信任 IP 地址段访问，并在服务端配置登录失败检测与速率限制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/862","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19666","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0991.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0991","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0991.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0991.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0991.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0991.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0824.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0823","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0823.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0990","title":"GNOME gdm VerboseAuth 信息泄露漏洞","description":"GDM（GNOME Display Manager）的 VerboseAuth 设置启用后，登录认证失败时返回的错误消息会区分\"用户不存在\"和\"密码错误\"两种情形，导致攻击者可通过枚举用户名的方式识别系统上的有效用户。此漏洞属于信息泄露类型，攻击者无需任何认证即可在本地或远程登录界面利用该漏洞，为后续针对性密码爆破或社会工程学攻击提供基础。影响范围涵盖使用 GDM 的各类 Linux 发行版。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0990"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-05T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:28.453","remediation":"在 gdm 配置文件中关闭 VerboseAuth 选项（置为 false 或删除该行），使登录失败时返回统一错误信息，防止枚举有效用户名。建议升级至 gdm 2.0 以上版本，该版本默认不启用 VerboseAuth。如无法立即升级，可在 SSH 或登录网关层限制登录频率并记录异常尝试。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0990","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0990.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0990.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0990","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0990.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/62aa382b460e7aee53e2fc9ebcfd565bebdac259/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0990.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0990.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0990.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88356/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0823.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0822","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0822.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0561","title":"Microsoft IIS 服务器端包含远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 服务器存在服务器端包含（SSI）功能安全缺陷，默认启用了 #exec 指令执行权限。远程攻击者可通过上传包含恶意 #exec 指令的 .shtml/.stm 文件至可写目录，触发目标服务器执行任意系统命令，导致完全控制服务器。该漏洞影响 IIS 4.0 及早期版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。微软官方已发布安全公告并建议禁用 SSI #exec 功能。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0561"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:38.580","remediation":"建议立即升级至 IIS 4.0 及以上版本并安装微软发布的安全补丁（如 MS99-023）。配置层面：在 IIS 管理器中禁用 SSI 的 #exec 指令，或完全关闭服务器端包含 (SSI) 功能。临时缓解：在防火墙层面限制对 Web 服务器的非必要访问，并监控异常 SSI 请求日志。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0561","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0561.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0561.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0561","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0561.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/62aa382b460e7aee53e2fc9ebcfd565bebdac259/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0561.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0561.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0561.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86059/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0822.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0822.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0821","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0821.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0560","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 系统文件权限漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统中关键系统文件或目录权限设置不当，导致低权限用户或本地攻击者可能读取、修改或删除系统关键文件，从而造成信息泄露、权限提升或系统崩溃。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及更早版本，攻击者只需拥有本地访问权限即可利用，无需特殊条件。攻击者可利用不当权限覆盖系统文件或获取敏感信息，严重威胁系统安全性。微软已在后续安全更新中修复此问题。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0560"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:38.460","remediation":"使用 Windows NT 资源工具包中的 cacls 或 xcacls 工具，将系统关键目录（如 %SystemRoot%、%SystemRoot%\\System32）的权限设置为 Administrators 和 SYSTEM 完全控制，Users 仅读取和执行。对于已停止支持的 Windows NT 4.0，建议升级至受支持的 Windows Server 版本以持续获取安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0560","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0560.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0560","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0560.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0560.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/62aa382b460e7aee53e2fc9ebcfd565bebdac259/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0560.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8954696320cbff8f7d95f98854cf0e72222fc646/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mwpg-5ghf-jf2p/GHSA-mwpg-5ghf-jf2p.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0560.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/8cfdaab2997679f3e193ea9539f778b75d8c9d41/1999.tsv","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0821.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0820","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0820.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0559","title":"Unix 系统关键文件或目录权限配置不当漏洞","description":"Unix/Linux 系统中关键文件或目录权限设置不当的安全问题。当 /etc/passwd、/etc/shadow 等系统关键文件或目录权限过于宽松（如全局可写）时，本地攻击者可利用不安全的权限配置读取敏感信息、修改系统文件或植入恶意代码，从而实现权限提升或完全控制系统。该漏洞源于未遵循最小权限原则进行配置，影响所有 Unix/Linux 衍生系统，攻击者只需本地访问权限即可利用，无需认证，危害严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0559"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:38.350","remediation":"立即检查并修复系统关键文件和目录的权限：使用 `chmod 644 /etc/passwd /etc/group` 和 `chmod 600 /etc/shadow /etc/gshadow` 恢复标准权限。对 `/bin`、`/sbin`、`/usr/bin` 等目录使用 `chmod 755`。建议定期运行 `rpm -Va`（RPM 系）或 `debsums`（Debian 系）审计文件权限异常。同时排查是否存在被提权的后门账户或 SUID 异常文件（`find / -perm -4000`）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0559","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0559.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0559.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0559","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0559.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/62aa382b460e7aee53e2fc9ebcfd565bebdac259/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0559.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0559.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0559.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86045/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0820.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0819","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0819.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0988","title":"SCO UnixWare pkgtrans 本地任意文件读取漏洞","description":"UnixWare pkgtrans 工具在处理软件包安装时存在符号链接漏洞，本地攻击者可通过创建恶意符号链接利用 pkgtrans 的权限以读取系统任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 SCO UnixWare 7.1 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高危。利用此漏洞需要本地系统访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0988"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:28.217","remediation":"SCO UnixWare 已停止维护，无官方补丁。建议迁移至受支持的 Linux 或 BSD 发行版。临时缓解措施：以 root 身份执行 `chmod 0755 /usr/bin/pkgtrans` 移除 setuid 位，阻断提权路径；同时通过 `chmod 0444 /etc/passwd /etc/shadow` 限制敏感文件权限，并仅在受信任用户可访问的受控环境中运行该系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0988","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19661","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0988.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/3701042200a4e64b9e2a7f3614e9e958db6af9cd/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0988.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0988","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0988.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/62aa382b460e7aee53e2fc9ebcfd565bebdac259/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0988.json","https://github.com/stg-tud/cveenhance/blob/6476e73d87cdc9cf610342ef15d131432ab41588/Annotations/Glanz/CVE-1999-0988.xml","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0988.md","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0988.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88365/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0819.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0818","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0818.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0556","title":"Unix 系统账户 UID 重复安全漏洞","description":"Unix/Linux 系统中用户权限控制基于 UID（用户 ID）而非用户名进行判断，当两个或多个系统账户被错误配置为相同的 UID 时，这些账户将共享完全相同的文件访问权限和资源所有权。此问题属于系统管理配置缺陷，攻击者可以利用共享 UID 的其他账户访问本不应授权的文件或资源，导致信息泄露或权限提升。该漏洞影响各类 Unix 发行版，需通过审计并修正账户 UID 配置进行修复。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0556"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:38.230","remediation":"使用 `awk -F: '{print $3}' /etc/passwd | sort | uniq -d` 检查重复 UID，对冲突账户执行 `usermod -u 新UID 用户名` 分配唯一 UID，并用 `find / -uid 旧UID -exec chown -h 新UID {} +` 更新文件属主。同时建立用户创建流程确保自动分配不重复 UID。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/876","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/3701042200a4e64b9e2a7f3614e9e958db6af9cd/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0556.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0556","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0556.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0556.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/62aa382b460e7aee53e2fc9ebcfd565bebdac259/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0556.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8954696320cbff8f7d95f98854cf0e72222fc646/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-573h-p65m-cffp/GHSA-573h-p65m-cffp.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0556.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--8053b2ad-2b59-4ec8-9ecf-84ad76b3b9bc.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0818.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0818.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0817","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0817.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0555","title":"Unix 操作系统非 root 账户 UID 0 权限提升漏洞","description":"Unix 系统中存在用户权限配置缺陷，系统管理员在创建用户时可能将非 root 用户的 UID 设置为 0（超级用户标识），导致该用户账号拥有与 root 同等的最高系统权限。本地攻击者可通过登录或切换至该具备 root 权限的账户，实现对系统的完全控制，包括读取/修改任意文件、安装后门、提权执行任意命令等操作。该漏洞影响早期多数 Unix 及类 Unix 操作系统版本，通常由管理员配置不当或系统被植入后门账号导致。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0555"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:38.127","remediation":"检查 /etc/passwd 中所有 UID 为 0 的账号，除 root 外立即删除或修改其 UID。建议使用 sudo 机制分配管理员权限，禁止共享 UID 0 账号，并定期审计系统账号权限配置。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0555"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0817.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0816","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0816.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0554","title":"Unix NFS 服务端 Export 配置不当权限提升漏洞","description":"NFS（网络文件系统）服务存在访问控制配置缺陷，管理员错误地将根目录（/）或密码文件等系统关键数据导出为全局可读，导致同一网络中的任意攻击者无需身份认证即可通过 NFS 协议远程挂载并读取这些敏感信息。该漏洞直接影响 Unix/Linux 系统中 NFS 服务的配置安全性，攻击门槛极低，可导致系统全部数据泄露。建议限制 NFS 导出范围并启用访问控制列表。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0554"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:37.323","remediation":"限制 NFS 导出的目录范围，仅导出必要目录而非根目录或敏感路径；在 /etc/exports 中使用 `root_squash` 选项压缩 root 权限，并指定允许访问的客户端 IP 或网段（如 `rw,root_squash,192.168.1.0/24`）；同时配置防火墙仅放行受信任来源的 NFS 端口（2049/TCP/UDP）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0554"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0816.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0815","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0815.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0551","title":"HP OpenMail 任意命令执行漏洞","description":"HP OpenMail 邮件系统存在安全配置缺陷，由于对打印请求的访问控制权限设置不当，拥有本地访问权限的攻击者可通过发送恶意构造的打印请求绕过安全限制，在目标系统上以 OpenMail 服务进程权限执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响 HP OpenMail 服务器，攻击者需具备本地用户权限，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0551"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:37.113","remediation":"限制 HP OpenMail 打印服务仅允许受信任用户提交打印请求，在 OpenMail 配置中禁用不必要的命令执行接口，并升级到厂商修复此问题的最新版本。同时在系统层面限制 OpenMail 运行账户的最小权限，防止恶意打印请求执行任意命令。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9804-078"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0815.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0814","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0814.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0550","title":"路由器路由表远程信息泄露漏洞","description":"部分路由器设备配置不当或存在权限校验缺陷，导致任意远程主机无需认证即可通过特定协议查询并获取路由器的完整路由表信息。攻击者可借此掌握目标网络的拓扑结构、子网划分及可达路径，为后续针对性网络攻击（如中间人攻击、路由劫持）提供侦察基础。该漏洞危害等级高，影响多种主流路由器设备，CVSS 评分 7.5。建议限制 SNMP 等管理协议的访问来源，配置 ACL 规则以限制路由信息查询权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0550"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:36.973","remediation":"在路由器上配置访问控制列表（ACL），仅允许信任的管理网段访问 SNMP、Telnet/SSH 及 Web 管理端口；关闭未使用的 SNMP 服务或将 SNMP 字符串设为只读并改用复杂 community 字符串；禁用路由协议的明文邻居通告（如 Cisco 路由器使用 `no ip route-cache same-interface` 配合 `distribute-list` 过滤路由表查询）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0550"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0814.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0813","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0813.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0549","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 重启后管理员自动登录漏洞","description":"Windows NT 操作系统存在自动登录配置缺陷，系统在注册表中以明文存储管理员密码。本地攻击者可通过读取注册表键值获取管理员凭据，进而获得系统完全控制权限。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及更早版本，需要攻击者具有本地访问权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0549"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:36.850","remediation":"在注册表编辑器中定位到 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\CurrentVersion\\Winlogon，删除 DefaultPassword 键值并将 AutoAdminLogon 键值设为 0；安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a 并使用 Syskey 工具 (Syskey.exe) 为 SAM 数据库提供额外加密保护；开启屏幕保护密码和 Ctrl+Alt+Del 安全登录要求。如业务允许，建议升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0549"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0813.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0812","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0812.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0548","title":"多款 NFS 服务器实现多余服务运行信息泄露漏洞","description":"目标系统运行了不必要的 NFS（网络文件系统）服务，虽然未导入或导出任何文件系统，但开放的 NFS 端口（2049/TCP 和 2049/UDP）可能被远程攻击者通过端口扫描发现并利用，导致系统信息泄露或攻击面扩大。攻击者可尝试枚举共享资源或利用 NFS 协议相关缺陷发起进一步攻击。建议关闭非必要的 NFS 服务以缩小攻击面。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0548"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:36.730","remediation":"立即停止并禁用不必要的 NFS 服务：在 Linux 上执行 `systemctl stop nfs-server && systemctl disable nfs-server`，在 Solaris 上执行 `svcadm disable nfs/server`。如需保留 NFS 功能，在 `/etc/exports` 中严格限制可导出目录及访问客户端（如 `192.168.0.0/16(rw)`），并使用 `exportfs -ra` 生效。同时配置 iptables 或防火墙仅允许可信 IP 访问端口 2049(TCP/UDP) 和 111(TCP/UDP)。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0548"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0812.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0811","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0811.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0547","title":"SSH .rhosts 文件认证漏洞","description":"SSH 服务器配置了 .rhosts 文件认证方式，允许基于主机信任关系的远程访问，而非强制要求密码或密钥认证。攻击者可通过伪造源 IP 地址或利用 DNS 欺骗绕过身份验证机制，在无需有效凭据的情况下直接获取目标系统的未授权远程访问权限。该漏洞影响大量未正确配置的 SSH 服务端，危害等级严重。建议禁用 .rhosts 认证方式，启用公钥或密码认证以消除此风险。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0547"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:36.623","remediation":"禁用 SSH 的 rhosts 认证机制，在 sshd_config 中设置 IgnoreRhosts yes 和 RhostsAuthentication no，并升级至 OpenSSH 3.0 以上版本（默认已禁用）。同时删除用户家目录下的 .rhosts 和 .shosts 文件，避免被用于权限绕过。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/315"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0811.toml"}]